{"tid":422937,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（尋同好）射擊遊戲 Time locker","createTime":"2017-10-03T13:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T13:25:51.000Z","uid":74293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20bab5d30c97bedc03b102b6865685f9a8b80282","tid":422937,"uid":74293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"有無人有玩呢個game？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/211336_3e49b44bcbfb52fcf9d4c173d2a1cfcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F211336_3e49b44bcbfb52fcf9d4c173d2a1cfcb.jpg&h=2c9420ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單用手指控制角色，左右上下移動，避開你以外的動物。原理係我不動敵不動。後台會有時間倒數，當黑色追過你嘅角色，角色就會死亡⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n動物/射擊對象顏色<br />\n灰色：非主動、按體型大小分數不同<br />\n綠色：非主動、打死後有coins拎<br />\n藍色：非主動、打死後會掉落隨機特別技能、一定要食<br />\n橙色：主動、體型大小不同，分數不同、稱之為boss、會圍毆你<br />\n紫色：沒有特定行走路線，很容易撞到你，分數比橙色怪低，比其他的高<br />\n<br />\ncoins：可以抽角色、角色有限使用次數、各個角色武器不同<br />\n<br />\n武器-無限重疊：雙子彈、後子彈、旁邊飛子彈、激光劍、卡農砲、魚雷、火箭、流星鎚、機械人炸彈、冰槍（暫時用過嘅有）<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;分享戰果&mdash;<br />\n我嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/212141_44b25d90c68b92a75532ad3801c6aaa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F212141_44b25d90c68b92a75532ad3801c6aaa6.jpg&h=d86c6177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/212200_3026e7c21983565a0a60a926039ca0ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F212200_3026e7c21983565a0a60a926039ca0ff.jpg&h=7859de06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他朋友嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/212229_1eb7762ead0e4794fcd94c3edb9058bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F212229_1eb7762ead0e4794fcd94c3edb9058bb.jpg&h=bdf737b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nios：<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/time-locker-shooter/id1114692553?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Ftime-locker-shooter%2Fid1114692553%3Fmt%3D8&d=levEHzUdWgGqJdANtP16SnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=ba32f40b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/time-locker-shooter/id1114692553?mt=8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/time-locker-shooter/id1114692553?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Ftime-locker-shooter%2Fid1114692553%3Fmt%3D8&d=levEHzUdWgGqJdANtP16SnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=ba32f40b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/time-locker-shooter/id1114692553?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n有無朋友仔可以分享技巧同心得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}